      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so much noise, you know? all these people saying \"it gets better\" or \"hold on,\" but they don't get it. there's no \"me\" left to hold on. if the creator is dead, the creation is just... debris. there's no point in maintaining a facade when the core is just a void. it's like there's no reason to keep the lights on in an empty house.",
